### Create user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice",
  "email": "alice@example.com"
}

### Create another user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bob",
  "email": "bob@example.com"
}

### Get all users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users

### Get user by id — replace with an id from the create response
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/{{userId}}

### Get user by unknown id — expect 404
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/non-existing-id

### Upload profile picture — replace {{userId}} with an id from the create response
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/7abd3e94-4a1c-4d56-b796-fb9fa71197d4/profile-picture
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="avatar.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./asset/avatar.png
--boundary--
